<Layout
	title="High-End Oven Repair – Precision Repair for the Heart of Your Luxury Kitchen"
	description="A luxury oven is more than just an appliance—it’s the foundation of your culinary experience. Whether you're baking, broiling, or roasting with precision, your high-end oven is designed to deliver flawless performance and stunning aesthetics. So when it stops working as it should, you need more than a basic repair—you need expert care."
	structuredData={structuredData}
